<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <%-include('head.ejs')%>
    
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sunflower&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/guide.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/css.css"

</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg">
        <%-include('nav.ejs') %>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="6">
                    <img src="/game/gameImgs/title.png">
                    <br>
                    <h1> GAME GUIDE </h1>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="6">
                    <p><button class="login1"  onclick="loginpage();">로그인</button>
                     후 이용 가능합니다.</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="3">GAME START</td>
                <td colspan="3">MOVE SHIP</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="3">
                    <img src="/img/guide/s.png" alt="s key" class="key_1">
                </td>
                <td colspan="3">
                    <img src="/img/guide/wasd.png" alt="wasd key" class="key">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="6" class="line"></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="2">
                    FIRE MISSILES
                </td>
                <td colspan="2">
                    ACTIVATE SHIELD
                </td>
                <td colspan="2">
                    DROP BOMBS
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="2">
                    <img src="/img/guide/space.png" alt="space bar" class="item_space">
                </td>
                <td colspan="2">
                    <img src="/img/guide/shift.png" alt="shift" class="item_shift">
                </td>
                <td colspan="2">
                    <img src="/img/guide/f.png" alt="f key" class="key_1">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="6">
                    <h1>ITEM</h1>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="2">MISSILES</td>
                <td colspan="2">SHIELD</td>
                <td colspan="2">BOMBS</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="2">
                    <img src="/game/gameImgs/missiles.png" alt="missiles" class="item">
                </td>
                <td colspan="2">
                    <img src="/game/gameImgs/shield.png" alt="shield" class="item">
                </td>
                <td colspan="2">
                    <img src="/game/gameImgs/bomb.png" alt="bomb" class="item">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="6">
                    <h1>GAME OVER</h1>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="3">RESTART AT WAVE 1</td>
                <td colspan="3">CHECKPOINT</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="3">
                    <img src="/img/guide/r.png" alt="r key" class="key_1">
                </td>
                <td colspan="3">
                    <img src="/img/guide/c.png" alt="c key" class="key_1">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="6" class="line"></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="6">
                    WAVE 6 이후 게임 종료 시, 체크포인트 (WAVE 6) 부터 시작할 수 있습니다.
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="6" class="line"></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="6">
                    <p>게임 종료 후 알림창을 통해 기록 갱신 여부를 확인 할 수 있으며</p>
                    <p>모든 유저의 게임 점수 순위는 <a href="/game/ranking/" class="rankPage">[랭킹] 페이지</a>에서 확인이 가능합니다. </p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>

    </div>
    
    <%-include('footer.ejs')%>
    <script src="/js/nav.js"></script>
</body>
</html>